id":279585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:50:56.000Z","msg":"Sogo 真特價！<br />\n<br />\n突發！Sogo 大特價，買$3000平$500！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086992\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論"},{"pid":"6ed0a19187661b408a5a45f0c27ede81b220bfb5","tid":2082484,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f775fcb58cd9169285b7d948810f2010e302ed","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:16:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b9af77ae77eddb814f2c6d2ce26a8c5ea40ad889","tid":2082484,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf752a21c3fc57e7fa02485f6efd7e29ef15a845","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b006bf266abd45eb37af084fa9028ea2cac2cf9","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9af77ae77eddb814f2c6d2ce26a8c5ea40ad889","tid":2082484,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:24:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:40:17.000Z","msg":"p<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4676913408be63e4a5b0775a393ec8d34f062775","tid":2082484,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"19b19c6b5881370e2d4059899fce3db428b934fd","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:40:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8861b113265094653aa7ef37c4dee69722af7aa8","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d9bc113beee91bf7edf9008666ec5b875139827","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e5859d2ee79eb9ef510e5602fc336efe0c554ec","tid":2082484,"uid":134153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:01:25.000Z","msg":"時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504d07dc0a1aa4e02f3de24abb2baae0664bd9d6","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67c7306ff7351bd5b5861d52d71b50108d9a8581","tid":2082484,"uid":108462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:03:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3c6f6ac47cdad4c5ffcb029cc65a0fea815121c","tid":2082484,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"<